name: DARKNESS
description:
Her body bathed in sunlight was a dance of colours, a mind-blowing spectacle ¿Could anything be so beautiful? Suddenly his gaze changed. He looked at me with distrust while I, with my arms stretched towards to the sky, waited for his return. My hands open and eager to touch him felt a breeze, the moment was near, but with a threatening impulse he pounced on my face, straight into my eyes, straight into my soul and straight into my heart !I have been betrayed! I'm afraid, it's dark, I'm alone again and there's no escape
